    "body": "Based on the Design System, The \"Gradient Cover\" component is using `customisation color 50`. The component is used in Wallet - Account Details [screen](https://www.figma.com/file/HKncH4wnDwZDAhc4AryK8Y/Wallet-for-Mobile?type=design&node-id=878%3A238236&mode=design&t=NTSx9HMnt9a0qhaL-1), and in Wallet - account switcher drawer/bottom [sheet](https://www.figma.com/file/HKncH4wnDwZDAhc4AryK8Y/Wallet-for-Mobile?type=design&node-id=838%3A216053&mode=design&t=NTSx9HMnt9a0qhaL-1) which uses `customisation color 50 - opacity 40`.  This variant/type is not captured in Design System. \r\n\r\nBased on the response from @mariocnovoa:\r\n\r\n> For now let's use the 50. I have to check it with Pedro when he comes back\r\n\r\nFor the time being, we will use `customisation color 50`.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n",
